+/**
+ * This is an implementation of the HMAC algorithms as defined
+ * in PKCS#12 v1.1 standard (see RFC 7292 Appendix B.4).
+ *
+ * @author Valerie Peng
+ */
+abstract class HmacPKCS12PBECore extends HmacCore {
